Ex3-0.2. Define Functions to Be Optimized

#Banana Function (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rosenbrock_function)
banana <- function(x1,x2){
    100*(x2-x1^2)^2+(1-x1)^2
}

#Eggcrate Function (https://www.al-roomi.org/benchmarks/unconstrained/2-dimensions/122-egg-crate-function)
eggcrate <- function(x1,x2){
    x1^2+x2^2+25*(sin(x1)^2 + sin(x2)^2)
}

#Golinsky's Speed Reducer (https://arc.aiaa.org/doi/abs/10.2514/2.1984)
golSR <- function(x1,x2,x3,x4,x5,x6,x7){
  0.7854*x1*x2^2*(3.3333*x3^2 + 14.9334*x3 - 43.0934) - 1.5079*x1*(x6^2 + x7^2)  + 7.477*(x6^3 + x7^3) + 0.7854*(x4*x6^2+x5*x7^2)
}
constGSR1 <- function(x1, x2, x3, x4, x5, x6, x7) {     
     1- 27/x1/x2**2/x3                
}       
        
constGSR2 <- function(x1, x2, x3, x4, x5, x6, x7) {     
     1 - 397.5/x1/x2**2/x3**2       
}       
        
constGSR3 <- function(x1, x2, x3, x4, x5, x6, x7) {     
     1 - 1.93/x2/x3*x4**3/x6**4     
}       
        
constGSR4 <- function(x1, x2, x3, x4, x5, x6, x7) {     
     1 - 1.93/x2/x3*x5**3/x7**4     
}       
        
constGSR5 <- function(x1, x2, x3, x4, x5, x6, x7) {     
     1 - ( ( (745*x4/x2/x3)**2 + 16.9*10**6 )**0.5 / (110*x6**3))
}       
        
constGSR6 <- function(x1, x2, x3, x4, x5, x6, x7) {     
     1 - ( ( (745*x5/x2/x3)**2 + 157.5*10**6 )**0.5 / (85*x7**3))   
}       
        
constGSR7 <- function(x1, x2, x3, x4, x5, x6, x7) {     
     1 - x2*x3 / 40     
}       
        
constGSR8 <- function(x1, x2, x3, x4, x5, x6, x7) {     
     1 - 5*x2/x1        
}       
        
constGSR9 <- function(x1, x2, x3, x4, x5, x6, x7) {     
     1 - x1/12*x2       
}       
        
constGSR24 <- function(x1, x2, x3, x4, x5, x6, x7) {        
     1 - (1.5*x6 + 1.9)/x4      
}       
        
constGSR25 <- function(x1, x2, x3, x4, x5, x6, x7) {        
     1 - (1.1*x7 + 1.9)/x5      
}       
        
constGSR10 <- function(x1, x2, x3, x4, x5, x6, x7) {        
     x1 - 2.6       
}       
        
constGSR11 <- function(x1, x2, x3, x4, x5, x6, x7) {

Ex3-1.1.2. Ten Simulations

time0 <- Sys.time()
for (i in 1:10){
  set.seed(i+1)
  GA.banana.t <- de(type = "real-valued", fitness = function(x) -banana(x[1],x[2]), lower = c(-5,-5), upper = c(5,5),monitor=F)
  if (i==1) {
    res <- GA.banana.t@summary[,"max"]
    final.obj <- GA.banana.t@fitness
    final.x <- GA.banana.t@population
  } else {
    res <- cbind(res,GA.banana.t@summary[,"max"])
    final.obj <- rbind(final.obj,GA.banana.t@fitness)
    final.x <- rbind(final.x,GA.banana.t@population)
  }  
}
